"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/show\"><code>show()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>События</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/merchantvalidation_event\"><code>merchantvalidation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/paymentmethodchange_event\"><code>paymentmethodchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/shippingaddresschange_event\"><code>shippingaddresschange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/shippingoptionchange_event\"><code>shippingoptionchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Наследование:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Похожие страницы для Payment Request API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLIFrameElement/allowPaymentRequest\"><code>HTMLIFrameElement.allowPaymentRequest</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MerchantValidationEvent\"><code>MerchantValidationEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentAddress\"><code>PaymentAddress</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentMethodChangeEvent\"><code>PaymentMethodChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequestUpdateEvent\"><code>PaymentRequestUpdateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentResponse\"><code>PaymentResponse</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">secure contexts (en-US)</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Payment_Request_API\">Payment Request API's</a> <strong><code>PaymentRequest</code></strong> interface the primary access point into the API, and lets web content and apps accept payments from the end user on behalf of the operator of the site or the publisher of the app.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"конструктор","title":"Конструктор","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"paymentrequest_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/PaymentRequest\"><code>PaymentRequest()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Создаёт новый <code>PaymentRequest</code> объект.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"свойства","title":"Свойства","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"paymentrequest.id_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/id\"><code>PaymentRequest.id</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Это значение изменять нельзя.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Только для чтения </span><span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Уникальный идентификатор для конкретного запроса <code>PaymentRequest</code>, который можно задать через <code>details.id</code>. Если ничего не задано, по умолчанию используется UUID.</dd>\n <dt id=\"paymentrequest.shippingaddress_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/shippingAddress\"><code>PaymentRequest.shippingAddress</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Это значение изменять нельзя.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Только для чтения </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>If requested via payment options, returns the shipping address chosen by the user for the purposes of calculating shipping. This property is only populated if the constructor is called with the <code>requestShipping</code> flag set to true. Additionally, in some browsers, the parts of the address will be redacted for privacy until the user indicates they are ready to complete the transaction (i.e., they hit \"Pay\").</dd>\n <dt id=\"paymentrequest.shippingoption_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/shippingOption\"><code>PaymentRequest.shippingOption</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Это значение изменять нельзя.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Только для чтения </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Возвращает идентификатор выбранного варианта доставки. Это свойство заполняется только в том случае, если конструктор вызывается с флагом <code>requestShipping</code>, установленным в значение true.</dd>\n <dt id=\"paymentrequest.shippingtype_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/shippingType\"><code>PaymentRequest.shippingType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Это значение изменять нельзя.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Только для чтения </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the type of shipping used to fulfill the transaction. This will be one of <code>shipping</code>, <code>delivery</code>, <code>pickup</code>, or <code>null</code> if a value was not provided in the constructor.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"методы","title":"Методы","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"paymentrequest.canmakepayment_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/canMakePayment\"><code>PaymentRequest.canMakePayment()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Indicates whether the <code>PaymentRequest</code> object can make a payment before calling <code>show()</code>.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"paymentrequest.show_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/show\"><code>PaymentRequest.show()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Causes the user agent to begin the user interaction for the payment request.</dd>\n <dt id=\"paymentrequest.abort_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/abort\"><code>PaymentRequest.abort()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Causes the user agent to end the payment request and to remove any user interface that might be shown.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"события","title":"События","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"merchantvalidation_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/merchantvalidation_event\"><code>merchantvalidation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>With some payment handlers (e.g., Apple Pay), this event handler is called to handle the <code><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/Reference/Events/merchantvalidation\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">merchantvalidation</a></code> event, which is dispatched when the user agent requires that the merchant validate that the merchant or vendor requesting payment is legitimate.<br>\n Also available using the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/merchantvalidation_event\"><code>onmerchantvalidation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> event handler property.</dd>\n <dt id=\"paymentmethodchange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/paymentmethodchange_event\"><code>paymentmethodchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>With some payment handlers (e.g., Apple Pay), dispatched whenever the user changes payment instrument, like switching from a credit card to a debit card.<br>\n Also available using the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/paymentmethodchange_event\"><code>onpaymentmethodchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> event handler property.</dd>\n <dt id=\"shippingaddresschange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/shippingaddresschange_event\"><code>shippingaddresschange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Срабатывает каждый раз, когда пользователь меняет вариант доставки.<br>\n Также доступно с использованием HTML атрибута <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/shippingaddresschange_event\"><code>onshippingaddresschange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"shippingoptionchange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/shippingoptionchange_event\"><code>shippingoptionchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Срабатывает каждый раз, когда пользователь меняет вариант доставки.<br>\n Также доступно с использованием HTML атрибута <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/shippingoptionchange_event\"><code>onshippingoptionchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"характеристики","title":"Характеристики","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/payment-request/#paymentrequest-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Payment Request API<br><small lang=\"ru\">Определение 'PaymentRequest' в этой спецификации.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Кандидат в рекомендации</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Совместимость с браузерами","id":"совместимость_с_браузерами","isH3":false,"query":"api.PaymentRequest","dataURL":"/ru/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Конструктор","id":"конструктор"},{"text":"Свойства","id":"свойства"},{"text":"Методы","id":"методы"},{"text":"События","id":"события"},{"text":"Характеристики","id":"характеристики"},{"text":"Совместимость с браузерами","id":"совместимость_с_браузерами"}],"summary":"The Payment Request API's PaymentRequest interface the primary access point into the API, and lets web content and apps accept payments from the end user on behalf of the operator of the site or the publisher of the app.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PaymentRequest","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"PaymentRequest","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ru/web/api/paymentrequest","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ru/web/api/paymentrequest/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web","title":"Веб-технологии для разработчиков"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/API","title":"Интерфейсы веб API"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/API/PaymentRequest","title":"PaymentRequest"}],"pageTitle":"PaymentRequest - Интерфейсы веб API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}